game.name: Spongebob Ear Surgery
game.description:
Are you feeling bored these days? Do you want to explore the doctor games during your free hours? Join Spongebob Ear Surgery game and allow yourself to play the role of an Otolaryngologist who has expertise of handling health issues related to ear, nose and throat! It will be amazing to conduct an ear surgery of your favorite character Spongebob. You are his family doctor, so he does not remember anyone except you when any sort of injuries comes to him. 

You advised him to consult you on a regular basis. But, he did not take it seriously and spent most of his time doing different kinds of pranks. The time passed and his problem in ear has also now become bigger. He has been suffering from this kind of problem for the last two years and has decided now to visit your clinic when his ear has begun to hurt. It is getting very difficult for him to withstand such kind of pain any longer. 

Take up the charge of an ENT specialist and be prepared to give him the urgent ear surgery in this html5 online game! Use the medical tools to remove all the bacteria from his ear! Follow all the needful 10 steps to make him able to hear properly again and enjoy with his lovely friends in Bikini Bottom once again! The instructions will be shown on the screen to help you make this surgery successful. Good luck to have a blast in our more surgery games for kids online on atmegame.com, no download required!
